{"id":"drug_ibu_001","document":"药品信息：布洛芬（Ibuprofen）为非甾体抗炎药（NSAID），用于缓解轻中度疼痛与发热。常见不良反应包括胃部不适、恶心。消化道溃疡活动期、严重肝肾功能不全等人群使用前应咨询医生。","metadata":{"kb":"drug","domain":"drug_monograph","drug_name":"布洛芬","drug_name_norm":"布洛芬","aliases":["Ibuprofen"],"source":"seed","source_id":"seed_drug_v1","lang":"zh","doc_type":"monograph","section":"overview","version":"v1","updated_at":"2026-04-14"}}
{"id":"drug_ibu_002","document":"用法用量提示（示例）：成人短期退热/止痛常按说明书或医嘱使用。避免超过推荐剂量或与其他NSAID同用。若有胃溃疡史、正在服用抗凝药或肾功能问题，应先咨询医生或药师。","metadata":{"kb":"drug","domain":"drug_monograph","drug_name":"布洛芬","drug_name_norm":"布洛芬","aliases":["Ibuprofen"],"source":"seed","source_id":"seed_drug_v1","lang":"zh","doc_type":"monograph","section":"dosage","version":"v1","updated_at":"2026-04-14"}}
{"id":"drug_asp_001","document":"药品信息：阿司匹林（Aspirin）具解热镇痛、抗炎及抗血小板作用。胃肠道刺激、出血风险是重要注意点。对阿司匹林/水杨酸盐过敏者禁用。儿童发热不应自行使用，以免瑞氏综合征风险。","metadata":{"kb":"drug","domain":"drug_monograph","drug_name":"阿司匹林","drug_name_norm":"阿司匹林","aliases":["Aspirin"],"source":"seed","source_id":"seed_drug_v1","lang":"zh","doc_type":"monograph","section":"overview","version":"v1","updated_at":"2026-04-14"}}
{"id":"drug_amox_001","document":"药品信息：阿莫西林（Amoxicillin）为青霉素类抗生素，常用于细菌感染。对青霉素过敏者可能发生过敏反应甚至严重反应，使用前需确认过敏史。抗生素需在医生指导下使用，不用于病毒性感冒。","metadata":{"kb":"drug","domain":"drug_monograph","drug_name":"阿莫西林","drug_name_norm":"阿莫西林","aliases":["Amoxicillin"],"source":"seed","source_id":"seed_drug_v1","lang":"zh","doc_type":"monograph","section":"warning","version":"v1","updated_at":"2026-04-14"}}
{"id":"drug_met_001","document":"药品信息：二甲双胍（Metformin）用于2型糖尿病血糖控制。常见胃肠道不适。肾功能不全、脱水或严重感染等情况下需谨慎，具体请遵医嘱。","metadata":{"kb":"drug","domain":"drug_monograph","drug_name":"二甲双胍","drug_name_norm":"二甲双胍","aliases":["Metformin"],"source":"seed","source_id":"seed_drug_v1","lang":"zh","doc_type":"monograph","section":"overview","version":"v1","updated_at":"2026-04-14"}}
